
         
         <p>The <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">ef-kassio</code> theme is now part of my <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">ef-themes</code> collection.  It is
a legible light theme with blue, red, magenta, and earthly colours.</p>

<p>Sample pictures are shown below.  Also check the entire set:
<a href="https://protesilaos.com/emacs/ef-themes-pictures">https://protesilaos.com/emacs/ef-themes-pictures</a>.  <strong>Click to
enlarge the image</strong> for best results.</p>

